script = ExtResource("1")
text = "[center]























Congratulations! You've reached \"The End\" of [u]Battle Deck Energy: Premature Release[/u].

Ahead are \"Unbalanced Lands\"!
There are some shelters back-to-back, two Spoiled Shits to build your deck, and then you'll face The Patriarch.

Then you'll lose.

If we never see each other again, thank you for playing!

If you'd like to follow the game's development (or branch the code):
Github: [url=https://github.com/Maaack/Battle-Deck-Energy]https://github.com/Maaack/Battle-Deck-Energy[/url] 
itch.io: [url=https://maaack.itch.io/battle-deck-energy-premature-release]https://maaack.itch.io/battle-deck-energy-premature-release[/url]

You've done all the beating and have already won, so don't take it too hard ahead!
















[/center]"
mood_type = "VICTORY"
